LET ME INTRODUCE MYSELF

Welcome to my portfolio page!

Put in front of a computer at an early age, I developed a deep curiosity and yearning to learn and to create software. In fact, some of my earliest memories are sneaking into my Dad's office to play games such as Charlie the Duck (2001) and Spider-Man (2000) - where I was not only deeply immersed in the worlds of those games, but also learning fundamental computer skills. This early interest extends to today, where I am consistently looking to learn new technologies and to improve my programming skillset.

I am most comfortable with Python, C++, and Javascript - with technologies such as Django, Flask, React, Node, Bootstrap, and Spring

Outside of programming, I am also an avid Music and Photography enthusiast.
Check out my Gallery page for a little snapshot of what I've taken!

FIND ME ON

Feel free to connect with me
